orized examination of the boy who lived|url =https://books.google.com/books?id=BoX-6R21MgQC&lpg=PP1&dq=Harry%20Potter&pg=PP1#v=onepage |publisher=BenBella Books |isbn=978-1-932100-88-4 }}\n* {{cite book |last =Silvester |first =William |year = 2010|title =Harry Potter Collector's Handbook |url =https://books.google.com/books?id=06FgsmilUXAC&lpg=PP1&dq=Harry%20Potter&pg=PP1#v=onepage |publisher=Krause |isbn= 978-1-4402-0897-3 }}\n{{refend}}\n\n== External links ==\n{{Spoken Wikipedia|En Harry Potter Wikipedia article.ogg|2011-01-02}}\n{{Wikivoyage|Harry Potter tourism}}\n{{Commons category}}\n* {{Wikia|harrypotter|Harry Potter}}\n<!-- Fan sites are covered within [[Harry Potter fandom]]. No need to include them again here. -->\n* [http://www.jkrowling.com/ J. K. Rowling's personal website]\n* [http://harrypotter.warnerbros.com/ Harry Potter movies]&nbsp;\u2013 Official website (Warner Bros.)\n* [http://harrypotter.bloomsbury.com/ Harry Potter] at Bloomsbury.com (International publisher)\n* [http://harrypotter.scholastic.com/ Harry Potter] at Scholastic.com (US publisher)\n* [http://www.raincoast.com/harrypotter Harry Potter] at Raincoast.com (Canadian publisher)\n* {{Worldcat id|lccn-sh99-3719|Harry Potter}}\n* {{Guardian topic}}\n* {{NYTtopic|complete_coverage/harry_potter|Harry Potter}}\n* [https://site.universalorlando.com/wwohp/ The Wizarding World of Harry Potter at Orlando resort, Florida]\n\n{{Harry Potter|state=uncollapsed}}\n{{J. K. Rowling}}\n{{BILBY Younger Readers Award}}\n{{BILBY Older Readers Award}}\n{{Good article}}\n{{active editnotice}}\n{{Subject bar|book=Harry Potter|portal1=Children's literature|portal2=Speculative fiction|portal3=Literature|commons=yes|commons-search=Category:Harry Potter|q=yes|q-search=Harry Potter (series)|b=yes|b-search=Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter|wikt=yes|wikt-search=Appendix:Harry Potter|d=yes|d-search=Q8337|voy=yes|voy-search=Harry Potter tourism}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Harry Potter| ]]\n[[Category:BILBY 