aughlin_PDF.pdf |title=Kyle Laughlin |publisher=Disney Consumer Products |accessdate=September 16, 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170105083856/https://a.dilcdn.com/bl/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2016/09/Laughlin_PDF.pdf |archive-date=2017-01-05 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n===[[Disney Publishing Worldwide]]===\n{{col-float}}\n* Core Publishing<ref>{{cite web|title=About Us:Disney Publishing Worldwide|url=https://www.disneyconsumerproducts.com/Home/display.jsp?contentId=dcp_home_ourbusinesses_company_overview_dpw&forPrint=false&language=en&preview=false&imageShow=0&pressRoom=DPW&translationOf=null&region=0|website=disneyconsumerproducts.com|publisher=Disney Consumer Products|accessdate=March 2, 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402165300/https://www.disneyconsumerproducts.com/Home/display.jsp?contentId=dcp_home_ourbusinesses_company_overview_dpw&forPrint=false&language=en&preview=false&imageShow=0&pressRoom=DPW&translationOf=null&region=0|archive-date=April 2, 2015|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n** Disney Magazine Publishing, Inc.\n** Disney Libri\n** Disney Libros (Spain)\n** Disney Book Group (Disney Book Publishing, Inc.<ref name=dta/>)\n*** Disney\u00b7Hyperion\n*** Disney\u00b7Jump at the Sun\n*** [[Disney Press]]\n*** Disney Editions\n{{col-float-break}}\n* Digital Publishing - Disney Book Apps\n* Disney Learning\n** Disney Educational Productions\n** [[Disney English]]\n** Disney Imagicademy\n{{col-float-end}}\n\n===Parks and resorts===\n* Disney Parks Merchandising\n** [[World of Disney]] Stores\n** Magic of Disney store - Orlando airport store<ref name=atm>{{cite news |title=PHOTOS: New Magic of Disney store now open at Orlando International Airport |url=https://attractionsmagazine.com/magic-of-disney-store-opens/ |accessdate=June 6, 2019 |work=Attractions Magazine |date=January 25, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190606135646/https://attractionsmagazine.com/magic-of-disney-store-opens/ |archive-date=June 6, 2019 |ur