perion (publisher)|Hyperion Books]]: sold to Hachette\n* [[GMTV]]: part owner; Sold to [[ITV plc]] and renamed [[ITV Breakfast Limited]] in 2009.\n* [[Miramax|Miramax Films]]: Sold to [[Filmyard Holdings]] in 2010 \n** [[Dimension Films]]: Retained by [[Bob Weinstein|Bob]] and [[Harvey Weinstein]] and absorbed into [[The Weinstein Company]] when they left Miramax Films\n* [[Power Rangers]] - Sold back to [[Haim Saban]] in 2010 alongside other shows related to it\n* [[Radio Disney Group]], sold off individual stations\n* [[WJRT-TV]], sold to Lily Broadcasting with WTVG\n* [[WTVG]]<ref name=\"sale\">{{cite web |last=Grego |first=Melissa |url=http://www.broadcastingcable.com/article/459382-EXCLUSIVE_Disney_to_Sell_Two_Stations.php |title=EXCLUSIVE: Disney to Sell Two Stations &#124; Broadcasting & Cable |periodical=Broadcasting & Cable |publisher=NewBay Media |date=November 1, 2010 |accessdate=September 16, 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121004234818/http://www.broadcastingcable.com/article/459382-EXCLUSIVE_Disney_to_Sell_Two_Stations.php |archive-date=2012-10-04 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n* [[Oxygen Media]]: part owner<ref>{{cite news|last=Petrozzello|first=Donna|title=The A Team|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-53381633.html|accessdate=December 30, 2012|newspaper=Broadcasting & Cable|publisher=Cahners Business Information|date=November 30, 1998|via=HighBeam Research|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924155346/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-53381633.html|archive-date=September 24, 2015|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n* [[E!]]: part owner\n** [[Esquire Network|Style Network]]\n* [[MovieBeam]]\n* [[Bass Anglers Sportsman Society]]\n* Walt Disney Studios Sony Pictures Releasing de M\u00e9xico\n* [[Fox Sports Networks]] - sold to [[Sinclair Broadcast Group]] and [[Entertainment Studios]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/disney-fox-rsns-sinclair-1203203930/|title=Disney Nears $10 Billion Sale of Fox Sports Networks to Sinclair|la